Mari Blanchard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mari_Blanchard 0 Mari Blanchard (born Mary E. Blanchard, April 13, 1923 – May 10, 1970) was an American film and television actress, known foremost for her roles as a B movie femme fatale in American productions of the 1950s and early 1960s.
